{
  "texts": [
    "Preprocess the images (resize, normalize, augment) and split into training and testing sets.",
    "This section evaluates the efficacy of the PolynetDWTCADx system at various levels of colorectal cancer detection and segmentation.",
    "Starting with the use of an integrated convolutional neural network (CNN) model, specifically RV-22 and DEV-22, on the CKHK-22 dataset, the evaluation procedure was a multistep process.",
    "We evaluated both of these models separately and in conjunction with the discrete wavelet transform (DWT) for feature extraction on the dataset.",
    "We improved the system's classification by transforming the features through a support vector machine (SVM)."
  ]
}